<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Contact Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #FFC107;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .message-box {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #FFC107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 15px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #FFC107;
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>New Contact Request Received</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>A new contact request has been submitted through the website.</p>
        
        <h3>Contact Details:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Name:</strong> <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= phoneNumber %></li>
            <li><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= subject %></li>
            <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= submissionDate %></li>
            <li><strong>Reference ID:</strong> <%= referenceId %></li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Message:</h3>
        <div class="message-box">
            <p><%= message %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Please respond to this inquiry as soon as possible.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
            <a href="https://preplings.com/admin/contacts/<%= referenceId %>" class="button">View in Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated notification from Preplings Contact Management System. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>